cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.LG 

This paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to improve the performance of health-related ads. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques to measure the improvements in click-through rates, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely sub-category. The paper also involves cybernetics (cs.CY), as it deals with the optimization of advertising campaigns using algorithms. Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely sub-categories.
